===Etymology===
From {{inh|en|enm|abrest}}, equivalent to {{prefix|en|a|t1=on, at|breast}}, in sense “breasts (chests) in line, side-by-side and exactly equally advanced”;<ref name="oetyld">{{R:Online Etymology Dictionary}}</ref> roughly “breast-by-breast”.

